.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, march, august, november, may
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, crime, romance, horror
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, tennis, soccer, volleyball
City: octobermaster, edinburgh, prague, paris, new-york
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, video-games, reading, dancing
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's birthday is in august
2. the person watching swedish movies is the person who's hobby is video-games
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is soccer
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is cycling
6. the person traveling to prague is the person who's hobby is writing
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to edinburgh
8. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle
9. the person watching romance movies is on the far left
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles
11. the person who's hobby is dancings is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh
12. the person traveling to octobermaster is the person who's sport is badminton
13. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to paris
14. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october
15. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday		|    may	|     october	|      august	|     march	|     november	|
| Movie-Genre	|   romance	|    martial-arts	|    fantasy	|    crime	|    swedish	|
| Hobby		|     puzzles	|    dancing	|     writing	|     reading	|      video-games	|
| Sport	|    volleyball	|     soccer	|     tennis	|    cycling	|      badminton	|
| City		|   edinburgh	|    new-york	|  prague	|    paris	|   octobermaster	|
